Package: heuristR
Title: R Client for Heurist Databases
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Robert J.",
      family = "Bischoff",
      email = "rbischoff@asu.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a session-oriented R client for working with Heurist
    databases. The package wraps Heurist authentication, metadata, and record
    retrieval endpoints and establishes a foundation for safe record creation
    and update workflows.
